            <div class="question-card" data-q="4">
              <div class="question-card__header">
                <span class="question-number">4</span>
                <span class="question-type-badge question-type-badge--long">Extended</span>
              </div>
              <p class="question-text">
                A student says: "Homeostasis only matters for body temperature — if you
                get too hot or cold, you die. Blood pH doesn't matter as much because a
                small change from 7.4 to 7.3 isn't really different."
              </p>
              <p class="question-text">
                Evaluate this claim. Use specific biological reasoning to explain why
